reviews.text: We came for lunch during weekend, surprisingly it's not full at all. There are a lot of lunch special set menu courses which are at very reasonable price. The stone pot fish fin or abalone sets are only 75 hkd. Other dishes like Milanese scallops is also very good with rosemary. The roasted pig skin is very crispy. Will definitely come back for dinner.

Good food n portions.  Service need to be improved.  I'll go back many times.  But they charge 200 for corkage fee.
BBQ pork, n sweet n sour pork are good dishes.
Nice, charming restaurant. Only disadvantage, it's on the first floor and the only way up are stairs.
Expensive, taste so-so except roast Suckling pig
Food was quite good. the presentation was done nicely. However, many of the items seemed to be out of stock

result.name: 城寨風味

reviews.text: 每個人有每個人喜好我到九龍城南角道城城寨風味小菜館服務態度可接受不過人客也不多但很吵耳🙈小菜方面很普通我叫咗很多小菜和一燉盅鮑魚和魚肚🤮只有燒乳鴿可以👌其他嘢👎👎
傳統懷舊口味👍

服務態度友善，會不停加水，非常有禮貌。

食物都算大份， 適合一家大細來食飯。 乳豬非常香口， 手撕雞味道還可以， 呢兩款菜式都係要預先留。 墨魚釀茄子炸到非常脆 加上醬汁十分惹味。
出品接受.空調不足.晚市時間，4人结賬1千多元。
食物質素一般，無乜味道，還吃到滿口油膩，最差是蠔仔粥，從沒吃過這樣貴又唔好食的蠔仔粥。價錢足可比美酒店中菜廳。唯一可讚是服務態度非常好。
